import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"high-performance-habits---brendon-burchard"}}>{`High Performance Habits - Brendon Burchard`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#high-performance-habits---brendon-burchard"}}>{`High Performance Habits - Brendon Burchard`}</MDXTag><MDXTag name="ul" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#personal-habits"}}>{`Personal Habits`}</MDXTag><MDXTag name="ul" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#seek-clarity"}}>{`Seek Clarity`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#generate-energy"}}>{`Generate Energy`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#raise-necessity"}}>{`Raise Necessity`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#social-habits"}}>{`Social Habits`}</MDXTag><MDXTag name="ul" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#increase-productivity"}}>{`Increase Productivity`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#demonstrate-courage"}}>{`Demonstrate Courage`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#sustaining-success"}}>{`Sustaining Success`}</MDXTag><MDXTag name="ul" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#beware-three-traps"}}>{`Beware Three Traps`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#the-number-one-thing"}}>{`The Number One Thing`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"personal-habits"}}>{`Personal Habits`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Seek Clarity`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Generate Energy`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Raise Necessity`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"seek-clarity"}}>{`Seek Clarity`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`"If you leave your growth the randomness, you'll always live in the land of mediocrity."`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`No goals, no growth. No clarity, no change.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`"Unhappiness is not knowing what we want and killing ourseles to get it." - Don Herold`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Is work just a job, an important career or a calling.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Enthusiasm + Connection + Satisfaction + Coherence = Meaning`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"generate-energy"}}>{`Generate Energy`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`There's perhaps no better way to increase ongoing happiness than to start a gratitude practice.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"raise-necessity"}}>{`Raise Necessity`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Four forces of necessity: identity, obsession, duty and urgency.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`When you are passionate about what you do, people understand. When you are obsessed, they think you're mad. That's the difference.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`This is the way high performers speak about their goals and their whys. They don't sound doubtful. They have confidence in the reasons they are working so hard and they are proud to tell you about their purpose.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"social-habits"}}>{`Social Habits`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components} props={{"start":4}}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Increase Productivity`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Develop Influence`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Demonstrate Courage`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"increase-productivity"}}>{`Increase Productivity`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`The fundamentals: setting goals and maintaining energy and focus. No goals, no focus, no energy - you are dead in the water.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Organise life into ten distinct categories: health, family, friends, intimate relationship, mission/work, finances, adventure, hobby, spirituality and emotion.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"demonstrate-courage"}}>{`Demonstrate Courage`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`"Only those who risk going too far can possibly find out how far one will go." - T.S. Eliot.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"sustaining-success"}}>{`Sustaining Success`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components} props={{"start":7}}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Beware Three Traps`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`The #1 Thing`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Summary Guide`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"beware-three-traps"}}>{`Beware Three Traps`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Keep telling yourself other people won't understand and it becomes a self-fulfilling prophecy.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`The exhausting, negative, emotional prison that is constant dissatisfaction saps performance. Perennial dissatisfaction is the first step on the path to misery.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"the-number-one-thing"}}>{`The Number One Thing`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Nothing correlates like confidence.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`You can not be congruent with something you've never defined. no clarity, no congruence, no confidence. It is that simple.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
